the Siete Partidas.

00:04:54.360 --> 00:04:55.660
&gt;&gt; Herrera: Las Siete Partidas.

00:04:55.660 --> 00:04:56.960
&gt;&gt; Dorn: Siete Partidas.

00:04:56.960 --> 00:04:59.470
Now it's very important,
crucially important publication

00:04:59.470 --> 00:05:03.560
in early Spanish law because while
it's a 13th century document,

00:05:03.560 --> 00:05:07.250
